TO SEE AVAILABE VIDEO FORMATS
youtube-dl -F <video_url>



TO DOWNLOAD THE VIDEO USING SELECTED FORMAT NUMBER OR ID
youtube-dl -f ID <video_url>



TO DOWNLOAD ONLY SUBTITLES
youtube-dl --all-subs --skip-download <video_url>



TO SEE AVAILABLE FORMATS FOR PLAYLISTS
youtube-dl -cit -F <playlist_url>



TO DOWNLOAD AUDIO DROM A SINGLE VIDEO
youtube-dl -x --audio-format mp3 <video_url>



TO DOWNLOAD AUDIO DROM ENTIRE PLAYLIST
youtube-dl -x -cit --audio-format mp3 <video_url>



TO UPDATE YOUTUBE DL
sudo pip3 install -U youtube-dl
